title: "pccx-lab — profiler, simulator, and trace report tooling for pccx"
abstract: >-
  Visual pre-RTL bottleneck profiler with a Rust/Tauri GUI, UVM
  co-simulation hooks, and trace/report generation for the pccx
  FPGA-oriented LLM inference accelerator stack.
type: software
license: Apache-2.0
repository-code: "https://github.com/pccxai/pccx-lab"
